            gameDescription: "Balatro is a 2024 poker-themed roguelike deck-builder where you play poker hands to score points and defeat increasingly difficult blinds. Each round you're dealt cards—make a pair, a flush, a full house—and multiply your score using Joker cards with wild effects. 'Blueprint' copies another Joker's ability. 'Hologram' adds a card to your deck. 'The Idol' multiplies score for specific suits. Each run is shaped by the Joker cards you're offered in shops, the deck modifications available (steel cards that give bonus chips, glass cards that multiply score but shatter), and the random hands you're dealt. You can't control what cards appear in your hand or what Jokers the shop offers between rounds—fortune spins its wheel with every draw, every shop refresh, every blind. Success comes from recognizing the patterns fate gives you and building a strategy around what luck provides. Sometimes you're dealt pocket aces and the perfect Joker to multiply them. Sometimes you're trying to make a flush work with scattered suits and no synergy. The wheel keeps spinning, and you keep adapting or you lose.",
