                meaning: "You're exhausted, you've been through so much, but you're still standing. Like Joel and Ellie pushing through the final stretches of their brutal journey across America, the Nine of Wands shows you battle-worn but not broken. You've faced challenges that have left scars—physical, emotional, or both. One more push remains before you can rest. This card acknowledges your fatigue while honoring your resilience. You've proven you can endure, and you're almost there. Don't give up now, even though every fiber of your being wants to. Draw on the strength you've already demonstrated. You've survived this much; you can make it through what remains.",
