                reflections: "• What confusion or problem needs the clarity of sharp analysis right now?\n\n• Where do you need to look more closely to reveal hidden truth?\n\n• What breakthrough insight is trying to emerge in your thinking?\n\n• How can you use your intellect and observation to cut through obstacles?",
